    "body": "I started writing these types because most of the lib are using `any[]` for the ABI for the last couple of years.\nMy types are not the long term solution, but maybe it can improve the current state on a short term. The optional fields should cover the different versions for now, until someone put some effort to write a script to generate the types dynamically. Or even better, before the solidity team generate them.\nHonestly if hardhat only implement the types for the ABI I would be very happy already ðŸ˜€",
